DeploymentInstructions.Value:
1. Configure kubectl:
   aws eks update-kubeconfig --region us-west-2 --name fraud-detection-dev

2. Deploy applications:
   cd k8s && ./deploy.sh

3. Access services:
   kubectl get services -n fraud-detection
